source: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTLANDMARK_00788_SYSTEM_000_200<tab>This appears to be a log with a board attached to it. How quaint.
target: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTLANDMARK_00788_SYSTEM_000_200<tab>Ce panneau de con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion est destiné aux édifices.

source: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTLANDMARK_00788_SYSTEM_000_300<tab>You may review the estimated time of completion for any landmark that is under construction by accessing the logboard in front of the appropriate plot.
target: TEXT_CTSMJICONSTRUCTLANDMARK_00788_SYSTEM_000_300<tab>Construire nécessite une certaine durée, que vous pouvez consulter sur le panneau de con<var 16 /var>struc<var 16 /var>tion. Soyez <var 08 E905 ((patiente)) ((patient)) /var> et profitez-en pour faire autre chose<var 1D /var>!
